CompanyDescription.label: Company Description
CompanyDescription.value: Sound Group Inc. ('Sound Group' or the 'Company') (NASDAQ: SOGP) is a global audio-centric social and entertainment company driven by a clear mission and vision: building the worlds largest audio platform to better connect and communicate. Leveraging its broad product portfolio and advanced in-house technologies, the Company caters to global user interest in audio entertainment and social networking. Sound Group is dedicated to shaping a future where audio not only bridges gaps but also amplifies human connection through the power of sound.
